'''韓亞航空162號班機'''（OZ162/AAR162）是一架由[[韓國|韓國]][[仁川國際機場|仁川]]飛往[[日本|日本]][[廣島機場|廣島]]的短程國際線的定期航班<ref>{{cite web|url=http://aviation-safety.net/database/record.php?id=20150414-0|title=ASN Aircraft accident Airbus A320-232 HL7762 Hiroshima International Airport (HIJ)|author=Harro Ranter|date=2015-04-14|work=aviation-safety.net|accessdate=2015-04-16|archive-date=2015-05-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150522072807/http://aviation-safety.net/database/record.php?id=20150414-0|dead-url=no}}</ref>，2015年4月14日，這架[[空中巴士A320|空中巴士A320]]進場高度過低，撞上[[跑道|跑道]]前端[[仪表着陆系统|儀表著陸系統]]的天線，左機翼和左[[發動機|發動機]]嚴重受損，側[[起落架|起落架]]機輪也受損，接著滑行到跑道旁的草地。機組人員在事故後放出逃生滑梯，疏散機上所有人，遇險乘客後步行至[[航站楼|航廈]]。機上81人中，無人罹難，27名乘客受傷，其中有1名受重傷。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://avherald.com/h?article=484c306e&opt=0|title=The Aviation Herald|work=avherald.com|accessdate=2015-04-16|archive-date=2015-08-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150816193621/http://avherald.com/h?article=484c306e&opt=0|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2015/04/14/asiana-airlines-skids-runway_n_7061700.html|title=Asiana Airlines Plane Skids Off Runway In Japan|work=The Huffington Post|accessdate=2015-04-16|archive-date=2015-04-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150416040905/http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2015/04/14/asiana-airlines-skids-runway_n_7061700.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |agency=[[Agence_France-Presse|AFP]] |title=Asiana plane skids off runway in Japan, leaving 20 injured |newspaper=[[The_Daily_Telegraph|The Daily Telegraph]] (online edition) |url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/travel/travelnews/11537093/Asiana-plane-skids-off-runway-in-Japan-leaving-20-injured.html |date=2015-04-15 |accessdate=2015-04-15 |archive-date=2015-04-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150415194625/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/travel/travelnews/11537093/Asiana-plane-skids-off-runway-in-Japan-leaving-20-injured.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

==事故飛機==
涉事飛機屬於[[韓亞航空|韓亞航空]]，飛機機型為[[空中巴士A320|空中巴士A320]]，註冊編號HL7762<ref>{{Cite web|title = ASN Aircraft accident Airbus A320-232 HL7762 Hiroshima International Airport (HIJ)|url = http://aviation-safety.net/database/record.php?id=20150414-0|website = aviation-safety.net|accessdate = 2015-04-15|first = Harro|last = Ranter|archive-date = 2015-05-22|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150522072807/http://aviation-safety.net/database/record.php?id=20150414-0|dead-url = no}}</ref>，於2007年10月12日轉交予[[韓亞航空|韓亞航空]]，在該次事件之後，此飛機因過度毀損而報廢。機長總飛行時間8233小時，副機長1583小時。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.airfleets.net/ficheapp/plane-a320-3244.htm|title=Asiana Airlines HL7762 (Airbus A320)|accessdate=2015-04-24|archive-date=2015-06-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150613225757/http://www.airfleets.net/ficheapp/plane-a320-3244.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.planespotters.net/Production_List/Airbus/A320/3244,HL7762-Asiana-Airlines.php|title=HL7762 Asiana Airlines Airbus A320-200 – cn 3244|work=planespotters.net|accessdate=2015-04-16|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150417003008/http://www.planespotters.net/Production_List/Airbus/A320/3244,HL7762-Asiana-Airlines.php|archivedate=2015-04-17}}</ref>

==事故發生經過==
日本[[國土交通省|國土交通省]]的航空局的大阪分部表示，機長試圖在黑暗與低能見度的情況下降落，且飛機無法使用[[儀表著陸系統|儀表著陸系統]]。在廣島機場，儀表著陸系統被安裝在東端，使得正常情況下，飛機都得從西邊降落。但是，因為風向，機長被航管員指示從東邊下降。以致飛機無法使用ILS。飛機進場高度太低，撞上ILS的天線，天線捲到機輪後導致機輪鎖死，接著機尾擦地。飛機在跑道中段約1500公尺處偏離跑道，最終在跑道旁邊的草地上停下。且飛機機鼻對著28號的跑道頭。<ref name=Shibun>{{cite news| author=| title=Police investigate airliner accident in Hiroshima on suspicion of pilot error| newspaper=[[Asahi_Shimbun|Asahi Shimbun]]| url=http://ajw.asahi.com/article/behind_news/social_affairs/AJ201504150086| date=2015-04-15| accessdate=2015-04-15| deadurl=yes| archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150415210850/http://ajw.asahi.com/article/behind_news/social_affairs/AJ201504150086| archivedate=2015-04-15}}</ref><ref name=WSJ>{{cite news| first1=Mitsuru| last1=Obe| first2=In-Soo| last2=Nam| title=Japan, South Korea Probe Asiana Plane’s Skid off Runway in Hiroshima| newspaper=[[Wall_Street_Journal|Wall Street Journal]]| url=http://www.wsj.com/articles/asiana-airlines-plane-clipped-communications-towers-before-veering-off-japan-runway-1429068123| date=2015-04-15| accessdate=2015-04-16| archive-date=2015-04-15| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150415202534/http://www.wsj.com/articles/asiana-airlines-plane-clipped-communications-towers-before-veering-off-japan-runway-1429068123| dead-url=no}}</ref>
<ref>{{cite web|url=http://news.carnoc.com/list/315/315111.html|title=韩亚航空OZ-162事故初探|author=罗石|work=http://news.carnoc.com/|accessdate=2015-05-29|archive-date=2015-06-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150601030126/http://news.carnoc.com/list/315/315111.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==事故調查==
日本[[運輸安全委員會|運輸安全委員會]]在事故後立即開始調查事故，廣島縣警方和韓方調查人員以及韓亞航空官方於隔天隨後加入<ref name=Shibun/><ref name=WSJ/><ref name="avherald">{{cite web|url=http://avherald.com/h?article=484c306e&opt=1024|title=The Aviation Herald|work=avherald.com|accessdate=2015-04-16|archive-date=2021-05-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210506153005/http://avherald.com/h?article=484c306e&opt=1024|dead-url=no}}</ref>。4月16日，調查人員即開始詢問機長和副機長事情發生的經過。一調查人員表示，下沉氣流可能會導致進場高度較低<ref name="Japan Times">{{cite news| author=| title=Downdraft may be factor in Asiana jet’s botched landing at Hiroshima| newspaper=[[Japan_Times|Japan Times]]| url=http://www.japantimes.co.jp/news/2015/04/16/national/downdraft-may-factor-asiana-airlines-botched-landing-hiroshima/#.VS9uwJTF8gA| date=2015-04-16| accessdate=2015-04-15| archive-date=2015-04-16| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150416115458/http://www.japantimes.co.jp/news/2015/04/16/national/downdraft-may-factor-asiana-airlines-botched-landing-hiroshima/#.VS9uwJTF8gA| dead-url=no}}</ref>。但機場天氣報告完全沒有任何不尋常的天氣或是風切變。當天只是一個普通的陰天。
